---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Logo Playground | èmote academy">
	<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-amber-50 min-h-screen">
		<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-teal-900 tracking-tight mb-4">Logo Concepts</h1>
				<p class="text-gray-600">Review the 4 SVG concepts below. Once you pick your favorite, we will drop it into the main header!</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				
				<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:shadow-md transition">
					<div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="h-16 w-auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#f43f5e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/>
							<path d="M14 9.5a2.5 2.5 0 1 0-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 0 5 0z M9.5 9.5h4" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-900 mb-2">1. The "e" Heart</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">A clean, modern heart integrating the 'e' from èmote.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:shadow-md transition">
					<div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="h-16 w-auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<path d="M12 16.5c-2.5 0-4.5-2-4.5-4.5S9.5 7.5 12 7.5s4.5 2 4.5 4.5-2 4.5-4.5 4.5z" fill="#f43f5e"/>
							<path d="M7 14.5l-3-3 2-2 3 3M17 14.5l3-3-2-2-3 3M12 21.5v-4" stroke="#0f766e" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-900 mb-2">2. Nurturing Hands</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Abstract teal hands gently supporting the rose heart of emotional intelligence.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:shadow-md transition">
					<div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="h-16 w-auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#0f766e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<path d="M19 11h-1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-5 0H11v-1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-5 0V11H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0 5H6v1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 5 0V16h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 5 0V14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 19 11z"/>
							<path d="M9 13 Q12 16 15 13" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
							<circle cx="10" cy="10" r="1" fill="#ffffff"/>
							<circle cx="14" cy="10" r="1" fill="#ffffff"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-900 mb-2">3. The Smiling Puzzle</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">A modern nod to your Wix site. Represents cognitive growth and happiness.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:shadow-md transition">
					<div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
					<svg class="h-10 w-auto shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
	<path d="M20 6.5C20 5.12 18.88 4 17.5 4C16.12 4 15 5.12 15 6.5H11C10.17 6.5 9.5 7.17 9.5 8V12C8.12 12 7 13.12 7 14.5C7 15.88 8.12 17 9.5 17V21C9.5 21.83 10.17 22.5 11 22.5H15C15 23.88 16.12 25 17.5 25C18.88 25 20 23.88 20 22.5H24C24.83 22.5 25.5 21.83 25.5 21V17C26.88 17 28 15.88 28 14.5C28 13.12 26.88 12 25.5 12V8C25.5 7.17 24.83 6.5 24 6.5H20Z" fill="#fcd34d"/>
	
	<path d="M18.5 4.5C18.5 3.12 17.38 2 16 2C14.62 2 13.5 3.12 13.5 4.5H9.5C8.67 4.5 8 5.17 8 6V10C6.62 10 5.5 11.12 5.5 12.5C5.5 13.88 6.62 15 8 15V19C8 19.83 8.67 20.5 9.5 20.5H13.5C13.5 21.88 14.62 23 16 23C17.38 23 18.5 21.88 18.5 20.5H22.5C23.33 20.5 24 19.83 24 19V15C25.38 15 26.5 13.88 26.5 12.5C26.5 11.12 25.38 10 24 10V6C24 5.17 23.33 4.5 22.5 4.5H18.5Z" fill="#fef3c7" stroke="#0f766e" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
	
	<circle cx="13.5" cy="11.5" r="1.5" fill="#0f766e"/>
	<circle cx="18.5" cy="11.5" r="1.5" fill="#0f766e"/>
	<path d="M13.5 15.5Q16 18 18.5 15.5" stroke="#0f766e" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
	
	<path d="M4 7V9M4 23V25M28 7V9M28 23V25M3 8H5M3 24H5M27 8H29M27 24H29" stroke="#0f766e" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
	<circle cx="2" cy="16" r="1" fill="#0f766e"/>
	<circle cx="30" cy="16" r="1" fill="#0f766e"/>
	<circle cx="16" cy="28" r="1" fill="#0f766e"/>
	<circle cx="16" cy="1" r="1" fill="#0f766e"/>
</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-900 mb-2">4. The Wise Owl</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">A friendly, educational mascot with a pop of rose coloring.</p>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>